# How to simulate this RTL code
Enter the folder and use the following command
    $ make

If you want to clean up the files that generate from source, please use the following command
    $ make clean


# How to synthesis this RTL code
If you want to synthesis the AES-128 RTL code, please use the following command
    $ dc_shell -f top.dc

However, the code after synthesis still has some bugs, you can try the following command and check the errors
    $ make syn

# How to change the plaintext and key
Open the testbench.v, In line 48~72 you can see the initialization of plaintext and key.

I have already created 
    1. random
    2. all 0s
    3. all 1s

You can choose one type and comment the others to try different patterns.


